  - Save the notification to the `notifications` table.
- **[NEW] `fetch_notifications_tool`**:
  - Pulls unread notifications for a specific recipient to show in the UI.

### [MODIFY] [mcp_server.py](file:///c:/Users/user/Documents/Hackathons/GenAI_APAC_Hackathon/backend/mcp_server.py)
- Expose the notification tools (send/fetch) to the MCP client.

